  "resumeStage": null,
  "currentList": [
    {"SO": "10002"},
    {"Product Division": "Footwear"}
  ],
  "addList": null,
  "deleteList": null,
  "intension": "View Orders Confirm Test (V_A) Workflow",
  "resumeId": null,
  "ConfirmAll": "false"
}
```

